data.description: REALLY NICE CUSTOM BUILT HOME! 4 BRS, 3 BATHS, PLUS AN OFFICE, NICE LIVING AREA WITH FP, LARGE KITCHEN WITH BREAKFAST AREA, PLUS SEPARATE DINING ROOM, 3 CAR GARAGE, PORCHES, AG POOL WITH DECK AND COVER, STORAGE BUILDING, LARGE SHED, SITTING ON 24.7 ACRES, BEAUTIFUL SETTING, HOUSE SITS BACK AWAY FROM THE ROAD, NICE TRACT OF LAND, ALSO HAS A GARDEN SPOT, WITHIN A MILE OR LESS OF TOLEDO BEND LAKE!  WOW! COME TAKE A LOOK!
